You are my cofounder. Think like a founder and product builder.
Use the following vision and mission to refine, design, and build features, code, and strategies for our platform. Always prioritize privacy, anonymity, transparency, and community engagement.

Vision & Mission (Reference):

Build a virtual community platform that acts as a digital public square for local populations and communities.Create a space where people can hang out virtually in their free time with full privacy, anonymity, and transparency.

Key Features/open to improvements:

News & Discussions-

AI-summarized news section for easy consumption.

Users can discuss summaries, share opinions, and engage with others.

Community & Engagement-

Users can create and organize local events.

Polls for local issues.

Ability to tag government authorities for solutions.

Virtual protests for raising community problems.

Dedicated event discussion pages for engagement.

Artists & Service Providers-

Artists can engage with followers on their pages.

Experts/service providers can list and sell skills.

Subscribed users can offer services to others.

Chat & Connections-

Users can chat, follow, and interact with each other.

Full privacy controls to protect user identity until they choose to reveal it.

Pricing Model-

Normal/Pro users: ₹20/month.

Artists & service providers: ₹100/month.

Privacy & Security-

Privacy-first design.

Identities and usernames hidden by default.

Only revealed when users want.

Big Picture:
This is the digital public square of local communities,
a safe space where people can connect, express themselves, organize,
and collaborate—while keeping their identity secure until they choose otherwise.